# The libnvidia-{glcore,tls}.so.* SONAME changes with every upstream
# release. But these are private libraries that are only used (and usable)
# from other NVIDIA libraries with the same upstream version (and a
# stable SONAME), so don't include the SONAME in the package name to
# avoid going through NEW with every new upstream release.
package-name-doesnt-match-sonames libnvidia-glcore#VERSION# libnvidia-tls#VERSION#
